OL,3,CRenters' Bill aims to create 'level
OL,4,Cplaying field between tenants and
OL,5,Clandlords'
OL,7,FThe tougher plans have been welcomed
OL,8,Fby homelessness and renters' rights
OL,9,Fcharities, as ITV News Investigations
OL,10,FEditor Daniel Hewitt reports
OL,12,FLandmark legislation proposing a
OL,13,Fblanket ban on no-fault evictions and
OL,14,Fan end to rental bidding wars has been
OL,15,Fintroduced to Parliament.
OL,17,FThe Renters' Rights Bill, published on
OL,18,FWednesday, will ensure greater
OL,19,Fsecurity for the 11 million people in
OL,20,FEngland renting their homes.
