OL,4,Cplaying field between tenants and
OL,5,Clandlords'
OL,7,FThe government said it will create a
OL,8,F"level playing field between tenants
OL,9,Fand landlords".
OL,11,FNo-fault evictions and mid-tenancy
OL,12,Frent hikes will be banned under the
OL,13,Ftougher plans, in a bid to crack down
OL,14,Fon "disreputable landlords".
OL,16,FThe plans must be approved by MPs and
OL,17,Fpeers, who could propose further
OL,18,Fchanges, before they become law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
