OL,7,FRenter groups have welcomed the bill,
OL,8,Fwhile landlords said the sector needs
OL,9,Fto be given "sufficient time" to
OL,10,Fprepare for the changes properly.
OL,12,F"Good landlords have nothing to fear,"
OL,13,Fsaid Housing and Planning Minister
OL,14,FMatthew Pennycook.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News, he said: "Many
OL,17,Fpeople live in completely substandard
OL,18,Faccommodation, for fear that a
OL,19,Fcomplaint will lead to a retaliatory
OL,20,Feviction.
