OL,7,F"We have to overhaul the regulation of
OL,8,Fthe private rented sector to ensure
OL,9,Fthey have the rights and protections
OL,10,Fthey need and deserve."
OL,12,F'The changes have been long overdue',
OL,13,Fsays Housing and Planning Minister
OL,14,FMatthew Pennycook
OL,16,FThe government has confirmed the
OL,17,Flegislation includes a blanket ban on
OL,18,Fno-fault evictions under section 21,
OL,19,Fwhich allows landlords to evict
OL,20,Ftenants with two months' notice
OL,21,Fwithout providing a reason.
