OL,7,FThe previous government pledged to end
OL,8,Fsection 21 evictions but concern about
OL,9,Fits impact on landlords and the courts
OL,10,Fwas set to lead to a delay in
OL,11,Fimplementation.
OL,13,FThe Conservatives' Renters (Reform)
OL,14,FBill then ran out of time to progress
OL,15,Fthrough Parliament before the election.
