OL,8,Ffurther than previously proposed by
OL,9,Fbanning section 21 evictions for both
OL,10,Fnew and existing tenancies, with
OL,11,Fresearch by charity Shelter finding
OL,12,F26,000 households have been evicted by
OL,13,Fbailiffs as a result of section 21
OL,14,Fproceedings since 2019.
